#: /app/specialAppInfoFakeDummyForL10nScript.php:4
msgid ""
"This is a Nextcloud app for structured personal data collection.\n"
"\n"
"If you are looking for a simple diary please take a look at the NextDiary "
"app or something similar. \n"
"\n"
"This app is made to collect a given set of values for later analysis on a "
"regular schedule. It is structured beyond what one would expect from a diary "
"and more like answering the same survey on a regular schedule.\n"
"\n"
"* Each diary consists of a given set of questions. \n"
"* The answers to these questions are collected as entries. Supported are\n"
"  * Text,\n"
"  * Boolean,\n"
"  * Rating (Stars 1-10) and\n"
"  * Float values.\n"
"* To allow back tracing of later changes the answers are editable, but keep "
"a history."
msgstr ""

